{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3ba91aaf2b","title":"中央首长接见首都红代会部分学校时的讲话","origin":"周良霄、顾菊英编《疯狂、扭曲与堕落的年代》之二——《十年文革中首长讲话传信录》, 2009。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"13876e5e7d","index":0,"year":1967,"month":12,"day":12,"articleId":"3ba91aaf2b"}],"tags":[{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"57eea82497","name":"康生","type":"人物"},{"id":"82305e518c","name":"江青","type":"人物"},{"id":"93cca4665d","name":"谢富治","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"e46e45351b","name":"陈伯达","type":"人物"},{"id":"ef71f03227","name":"中央文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"421124ccd3","name":"江青"},{"id":"48606ca4e5","name":"陈伯达"},{"id":"7a99cebe4e","name":"周恩来"},{"id":"85b13f5c0b","name":"谢富治"},{"id":"8bb7755376","name":"康生"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2d60bbdd1c","type":"title","text":"中央首长接见首都红代会部分学校时的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3ba91aaf2b"},{"id":"6a1c6dd04e","type":"authors","text":"谢富治康生周恩来陈伯达江青","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3ba91aaf2b"},{"id":"0aa2ff48ac","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月十二日晚，周总理、陈伯达、康生、江青、戚本禹、姚文元、谢富治、吴法宪、杨成武、汪东兴、吴德、丁国钰、黄作珍等同志，在人民大会堂安徽厅，接见了首都红代会的部分学校，现将领导同志在座谈中的一些讲话，发表如下：","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3ba91aaf2b"},{"id":"eda6891fa5","type":"paragraph","text":"谢富治同志：现在开会，总理及中央文革小组同志接见，听听同志们的汇报，有什么问题、经验介绍一下，以后还要开一次。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3ba91aaf2b"},{"id":"fa8f86e5a2","type":"paragraph","text":"(首先由林院汇报，当汇报到胡仁奎问题时)","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3ba91aaf2b"},{"id":"d6626273c9","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：胡仁奎是老特务了，他老婆也是特务。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3ba91aaf2b"},{"id":"d820a21657","type":"paragraph","text":"(众答：已经逮起来了。)","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3ba91aaf2b"},{"id":"a9715c5118","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：他是谁派去的？(林院：是彭真、薄一波派到林学院去的。)","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3ba91aaf2b"},{"id":"f9ec486b8e","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：什么时候来的，怎么我五八年到林院没有见过他。(答：后来派去的。)","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3ba91aaf2b"},{"id":"aa3fa675a4","type":"paragraph","text":"(林院继续汇报，当谈到教改问题时)","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3ba91aaf2b"},{"id":"ec6fe2cd6c","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：你们林院后面挖湖造山造成没有？(早造成了。)(总理听不懂，代表向总理解释。)","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3ba91aaf2b"},{"id":"698873730e","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：真不象样子。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3ba91aaf2b"},{"id":"8ef9b19442","type":"paragraph","text":"(当林院汇报到今年党组有十一个成员，由六个正式党员，五个非党员组成时。)","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3ba91aaf2b"},{"id":"12160fea89","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：有五个非党员，怎么叫党组？(林院向康老解释。)你们五个人还履行不履行手续？","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3ba91aaf2b"},{"id":"3aecbcf739","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：支部通过？核心组讨论？那是非共产党员批准共产党员。手续要健全，还得填表。","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3ba91aaf2b"},{"id":"bda0e3d71d","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：要不然再来一次文化大革命，人家会说你没有入党，那就糟了。(众笑)要有介绍人，否则将来人家否认。","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3ba91aaf2b"},{"id":"4437862e5e","type":"paragraph","text":"伯达：手续要搞好，介绍人要清楚，要有组织批准。","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3ba91aaf2b"},{"id":"a6a5161f53","type":"paragraph","text":"(林院继续汇报教改情况)","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3ba91aaf2b"},{"id":"adf299148e","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：你们考虑过这些问题没有，你们学校到底在什么地方好？到山区、林区呢？还是留在北京挖湖造山。","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3ba91aaf2b"},{"id":"e626a655d9","type":"paragraph","text":"代表答：准备迁到西北去。总理点点头。","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3ba91aaf2b"},{"id":"3df0b92809","type":"paragraph","text":"代表问：我们什么时候搬？","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3ba91aaf2b"},{"id":"e35149a325","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：先把方案提上来。","index":21,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3ba91aaf2b"},{"id":"bc28c78c49","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：林院总得搬到林区去。","index":22,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3ba91aaf2b"},{"id":"208f44f360","type":"paragraph","text":"(北航汇报情况)","index":23,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3ba91aaf2b"},{"id":"6245aafbd5","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：你们对武光怎么看法？(答：我们对他看法还不错。)","index":24,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3ba91aaf2b"},{"id":"843f8676b6","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：我和你们早打过招呼，可你们一直都在保护他，这就不对啊！","index":25,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3ba91aaf2b"},{"id":"cba9c2ae5d","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：不行！他是大叛徒、特务、假共产党员。","index":26,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3ba91aaf2b"},{"id":"900deab192","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：我在武汉和井冈山打过招呼，告诉过你们，你们不听嘛！","index":27,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3ba91aaf2b"},{"id":"80e6566e8b","type":"paragraph","text":"(邮电学院汇报)","index":28,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3ba91aaf2b"},{"id":"1a78b56689","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：听说在邮电学院设立过秘密电台，有没有这回事？(回答讲：设立过电台。)私设电台是犯法的，部队设电台要请示批准。邮电学院学技术，搞秘密电台，波长和呼号都不清楚，这是你们的电台还是敌人的电台，造成混乱现象。尤其是邮电学院，你们学了一点技术，就用国家器材，这就不对了。(邮电学院代表回答：我们保证以后不再搞了。)你们要严肃对待这个问题。","index":29,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3ba91aaf2b"},{"id":"f5b12addca","type":"paragraph","text":"(邮电学院汇报到他们学术权威进行考试时)","index":30,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3ba91aaf2b"},{"id":"abf25120a7","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：你们也是突然袭击。","index":31,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3ba91aaf2b"},{"id":"7c12e09ae4","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：不许人家这样考试你们，你们又在考试人家。(众笑。)","index":32,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3ba91aaf2b"}],"page":{"id":"d540a2d0f7","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3ba91aaf2b","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}